# compliance-engine

The compliance engine implements critical regulatory controls for mortgage industry contact management:

## TCPA Compliance Controls
Location: pages/Product.tsx
- Enforces Telephone Consumer Protection Act (TCPA) requirements 
- Validates consent before automated contact attempts
- Maintains audit trail of consent records
- Implements required opt-out mechanisms

## Contact Window Management
- Restricts outbound contact attempts to 8am-9pm in recipient's local timezone
- Handles timezone calculations and daylight savings transitions
- Enforces state-specific restrictions (e.g. Louisiana Sunday calling prohibition)

## DNC Integration 
- Real-time Do Not Call list validation before contact attempts
- Integration with national DNC registry
- Maintains company-specific DNC list
- Automated suppression of DNC-registered numbers

## Regulatory Features
- State-specific compliance rule enforcement
- Consent expiration tracking
- Required disclosure management
- Automated compliance reporting capabilities

